name: Transcend
description:
"Where the grey and weeping ocean fought above the dunes, the blowing sand transformed the horizon and blurred two worlds. As the warm, soft melodies fade into the distance, I feel my body go limp and I breathe deeply, knowing the fear that is to come." - Sykcolo / AI

Transcend by @Sykcoloart

Taking something that most would consider ugly or repulsive and showing it in a different way that transforms it into something uniquely beautiful is the main passion behind this project that I called Metamorphoses.

This artwork is created using generative techniques to mutate and deconstruct a micrograph of flower senescence. 

Learn about the inspiration, story and techniques behind this project on my website: https://www.sykcolo.com/blog-1/the-metamorphoses-collection
